Learn To Master Nuendo!
This Nuendo training CD-ROM covers key operational techniques and the new features of Nuendo 3.0. Every major topic is covered, including Setup, Project Management, Recording, Editing, Arranging, Mixing, Processing, Virtual Instruments, Synchronization, Advanced Uses, and Tips. If you&amp;#039;re a new Nuendo user you can use this to get up to speed with Nuendo quickly and easily. The Introduction alone takes you through set-up, first record, edit, and mix.

These Nuendo movie tutorials include not only basic functions of the software, but also cover production techniques, special shortcuts, key commands, and before and after audio examples. More than four hours of video instruction are included! Key tutorials include Using the Pool, Loop recording, Track Automation, Latency &amp; Timing, Instrument Track, The VST Instrument Rack, Freeze Function, VST System Link, Surround, and more !

